               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <t:locus xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" from="3v" to="21r">3v-21r</t:locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s21IHA">قران, Fourteenth ǧuz’ (14/30)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <t:locus xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" target="#3v">-3v</t:locus>بِسْمِ اللهِ الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيْمِ اَلَرَ تِلْكَ اَيَاتُ الكِتَابِ وَ قُرأَنٍ مُّبِيْنٍ رُبّمَا يَوَدُّ  
الّذِيْنَ \كَفَرُوْا<note>Last word added in the margin after the text was checked.</note>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <t:locus xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" target="#21r">-21r</t:locus>اِنَّ اللهَ مَعَ الّذِيْنَ اتِّقَوْا وَالّذِيْنَ هُمْ مُّحْسِنُوْنَ</explicit>
                     <note>15:1-16:128. Irregular ihmāl signs (rā’s). 12 to 13 lines a page. Rubricated title of suras. Words completed the following line on almost all folios. Words, which were started on a line, were entirely rewritten the following line in a lot of places. Deletions, and corrections after revision. Few margins, saǧda mark in red (13r).</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
